[thinking] **Considering Spring Boot metrics**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about whether to include `spring-boot-micrometer-observation`. The docs suggest referring to Boot Metrics/Tracing for enabling those features. To test auto configuration, I can manually provide MeterRegistry and Tracer beans. If I consider typical user scenarios, including Spring Boot actuator and Micrometer seems important. However, I need to be careful since Boot 4.1 RC might not be compatible with the Java 21 repo setup. I'll also need to check the `spring-ai-client-chat` for `ChatModelMeterObservationHandler`.
